<paragraph id="IFRS16_69" base="F45929494"><paranum>69</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRSÂ 16"/><data name="paranum" value="69"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS16_P0255"><xref base="F45929669" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0360">Initial direct costs<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0182"/></ph></xref>,  other than those incurred by manufacturer or dealer <xref base="F45929747" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0382">lessors<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0222"/></ph></xref>, are included in the initial measurement of the <xref base="F45929758" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0383">net investment in the lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0256"/></ph></xref> and reduce the amount of income recognised over the <xref base="F45929725" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0376">lease term<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0218"/></ph></xref>. The <xref base="F45929676" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0362">interest rate implicit in the lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0195"/></ph></xref> is defined in such a way that the initial direct costs are included automatically in the net investment in the lease; there is no need to add them separately.</p></body></paragraph>